Installation
============

    # Clone the git repository
    git clone git://github.com/johnthedebs/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    # Link in the .vimrc file
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    # Set up the submodules
    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

